{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "feishu-flow-kit-v1",
    "name": "Feishu Flow Kit — API Demo",
    "description": "Postman collection for testing feishu-flow-kit endpoints locally or in production.\n\n## Setup\n\n1. **Import** this file into Postman (File → Import → select JSON)\n2. **Clone the environment** and configure variables below\n3. Run requests in the **Setup First** folder before testing webhooks\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Example | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `base_url` | `http://localhost:8787` | Bot server base |\n| `webhook_path` | `/webhook` | Webhook endpoint path |\n| `app_id` | `cli_xxx` | Feishu app ID |\n| `app_secret` | `xxx` | Feishu app secret |\n| `verification_token` | `xxx` | Feishu event verification token |\n| `encrypt_key` | `xxx` | Encryption key (if enabled) |\n| `feishu_api_base` | `https://open.feishu.cn` | Feishu API base URL |\n| `tenant_access_token` | (auto) | Set by \"Get Tenant Token\" pre-request |\n\n## Notes\n\n- Requests tagged **Auth Required** need a valid `tenant_access_token`\n- Use the ** Feishu API Auth** pre-request script to auto-refresh tokens\n- Message simulation requires a real `event_id` from a prior Feishu event",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8787"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhook_path",
      "value": "/webhook"
    },
    {
      "key": "app_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "app_secret",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "verification_token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "encrypt_key",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "feishu_api_base",
      "value": "https://open.feishu.cn"
    },
    {
      "key": "tenant_access_token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{tenant_access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🛠️ Setup First",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Tenant Access Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "// Refresh tenant token before each request",
                  "const baseUrl = pm.environment.get('feishu_api_base') || 'https://open.feishu.cn';",
                  "const appId = pm.environment.get('app_id');",
                  "const appSecret = pm.environment.get('app_secret');",
                  "",
                  "if (!appId || !appSecret) {",
                  "  console.log('app_id or app_secret not set — skipping token fetch');",
                  "  return;",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "const getToken = () => {",
                  "  const response = pm.sendRequest({",
                  "    url: `${baseUrl}/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`,",
                  "    method: 'POST',",
                  "    header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },",
                  "    body: {",
                  "      mode: 'raw',",
                  "      raw: JSON.stringify({ app_id: appId, app_secret: appSecret })",
                  "    }",
                  "  });",
                  "  return response;",
                  "};",
                  "",
                  "getToken().then(resp => {",
                  "  if (resp.code === 0 || resp.status === 200) {",
                  "    const data = resp.json();",
                  "    if (data.tenant_access_token) {",
                  "      pm.environment.set('tenant_access_token', data.tenant_access_token);",
                  "      console.log('Token refreshed:', data.tenant_access_token.slice(0, 10) + '...');",
                  "    }",
                  "  } else {",
                  "    console.warn('Token fetch failed:', resp.status, resp.json());",
                  "  }",
                  "}).catch(err => console.warn('Token fetch error:', err));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "name": "Get Tenant Access Token",
            "request": {
              "url": "{{feishu_api_base}}/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal",
              "method": "POST",
              "header": [
                {
                  "key": "Content-Type",
                  "value": "application/json"
                }
              ],
              "body": {
                "mode": "raw",
                "raw": "{\n    \"app_id\": \"{{app_id}}\",\n    \"app_secret\": \"{{app_secret}}\"\n}"
              },
              "description": "Fetches a tenant access token from Feishu. This is automatically run before requests that need auth."
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
